{"tid":1591752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Ann 姐(蔣麗芸): “太子站死人係「假新聞」，冇人向我求助！」","createTime":"2019-09-24T09:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:16:58.000Z","uid":226548,"like":13,"dislike":246,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"8a026449c10db713430bc888c1191bb2217c2f17","tid":1591752,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190707/_2019070709313176122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190707%2F_2019070709313176122.jpg&h=14d8c0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】太子站8．31事件過後，唔少傳言話有人被警察毆打至死，甚至有指有6人斷頸亡；民建聯立法會議員<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蔣麗芸（Ann姐）早前呼籲死者家屬搵佢求助，佢噚日就話呼籲咗3個星期都冇人聯絡佢</span></strong>，加上問過局方都話冇事，所以認為係假新聞，但呢類消息令唔少年輕人、小朋友以為有人身亡而傷心流淚，「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢類煽情假新聞，搞到太子站垃圾堆咁</span></strong>，啲嘢爛晒，應唔應該立法（規管假新聞）？政府應該認真考慮」。"},{"pid":"b9f1f79b848186aa682c22d4419f48e445c54ac9","tid":1591752,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:43:02.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20190924/s00002/1569263906971/【emily】冇收求助-ann姐-太子站死人係假新聞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190924%2Fs00002%2F1569263906971%2F%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E5%86%87%E6%94%B6%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9-ann%E5%A7%90-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%82%E5%81%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=e21f80d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190924%2Fs00002%2F1569263906971%2F%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E5%86%87%E6%94%B6%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9-ann%E5%A7%90-%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E4%BF%82%E5%81%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E&h=4ec852c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/2